# AioFauna

ðŸš€ Introducing aiofauna: A full-stack framework built on top of Aiohttp, Pydantic and FaunaDB.

ðŸ”¥ Inspired by FastAPI focuses on Developer Experience, Productivity and Versatility.

ðŸŒŸ Features:

âœ… Supports Python 3.7+, comes with an opinionated ODM (Object Document Mapper) out of the box for FaunaDB that abstracts out complex FQL expressions into pythonic, fully typed asynchronous methods for all CRUD operations.

âœ… Powerful and Scalable: Being built on top of Aiohttp an asyncio based http server/client and FaunaDB an scalable serverless database for modern applications allows for powerful and seamless integrations.

âœ… Performant: As a framework built on top of Aiohttp it leverages the power of asyncio and the fastest python `HTTPClient` aiohttp plus the ubiquiness of FaunaDB to achieve high performance.

âœ… Automatic Swagger UI generation: Automatic generation of interactive Swagger UI documentation for instant testing of your `Api`.

âœ… SSE (Server Sent Events): Built-in support for SSE (Server Sent Events) for real-time streaming of data from FaunaDB to your application.

âœ… Websockets: Built-in support for Websockets for real-time bidirectional communication between your application and the resources served by AioFauna `Api`.

âœ… Robust data validation: Utilizes the rich features of Pydantic for data validation and serialization.

âœ… Auto-provisioning: Automatic management of indexes, unique indexes, and collections with `FaunaModel` ODM.

âœ… Full JSON communication: Focus on your data, don't worry about the communication protocol. Your `Api` will receive and return JSON.

âœ… Markdown and Html support with live reload: experiment an smooth frontend devserver experience without leaving your backend code with familiar syntax, `render_template` and `markdown_it` functions enable you to render static markdown files and html jinja templates with live reload.

âœ… Inspired by fastapi, you will work with almost the same syntax and features like path operations, path parameters, query parameters, request body, status codes, `/docs` automatic interactive API documentation, and decorated view functions and automatic serialization and deserialization of your data.

ðŸ’¡ With aiofauna, you can build fast, scalable, and reliable modern applications, avoiding decision fatigue and focusing on what really matters, your data and your business logic.

ðŸ“š Check out the aiofauna library, and start building your next-gen applications today! ðŸš€

#Python #FaunaDB #Async #Pydantic #aiofauna

